#

Cucumber Mint Cooler

10 min
$3
50 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

AmericanMediterranean

Course:

BeverageAppetizer

Tags:

DrinkRefreshingSummerEasy

Description

A refreshing and hydrating drink perfect for hot days, combining crisp cucumber and fragrant mint.

Ingredients

  • cucumber: 1 medium
  • fresh mint leaves: 1/4 cup
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • honey or agave syrup: 1-2 tablespoons
  • water: 2 cups
  • ice cubes: as needed
